divs: Sighting Detailspulled up to a red light in my car, as i stopped i saw coming out of the eastern sky a green fireball. it traveled west and disappeared over the horizon. thought it was a plane at first but the descent angle was too steep for that. possibly a meteor due to its trajectory, angle of descent and such. the driver in the car next to mine saw it as well judging by his reaction.
Summary: green fireball over miami FL (kendall area)
